WEBVTT

00:02.936 --> 00:04.772
[ Quacking ]

00:05.573 --> 00:07.275
[ Warble, zap! ]

00:08.542 --> 00:11.045
[ Roars ]

00:13.747 --> 00:14.848
♪ "Adventure Time"

00:14.882 --> 00:16.217
♪ Come on, grab your friends

00:16.250 --> 00:19.019
♪ We'll go to very
messed-up lands ♪

00:19.053 --> 00:21.322
♪ With Finn and Jake,
Ice King, and Betty ♪

00:21.355 --> 00:22.890
♪ Who knows how it will end?

00:27.528 --> 00:28.028
♪♪

00:33.867 --> 00:35.903
[ Indistinct chanting ]

00:35.936 --> 00:37.905
Flame Crowd:
Smash the nerds!

00:37.938 --> 00:39.440
Smash the nerds!

00:39.473 --> 00:41.742
Nerds, nerds,
smash the nerds!

00:41.775 --> 00:44.078
A nerdless world
is the best kind of world!

00:44.112 --> 00:46.380
Nerd, nerds, no more nerds!

00:46.414 --> 00:48.082
[ Grunting ]
Heh...hah...

00:48.116 --> 00:49.883
Heh...hah...

00:49.917 --> 00:52.420
Heh...hah...hah...

00:52.453 --> 00:53.387
Finn!

00:53.421 --> 00:55.055
Fight, fight, fight.

00:55.089 --> 00:56.557
Finn, stop.

00:56.590 --> 00:59.026
What happened to getting
the fire jewel and saving Ooo?

00:59.059 --> 01:01.061
Is this about you ex?

01:01.095 --> 01:03.431
This is about
the purity of battle.

01:03.464 --> 01:07.601
Okay, but you usually have
a reason for fighting.

01:07.635 --> 01:10.438
The fiery heartbeat of battle
is its own reason.

01:10.471 --> 01:12.440
No, that's stupid.

01:12.473 --> 01:13.874
-Yah!
-Oh, Glob!

01:13.907 --> 01:16.477
Just listen to the beat
of your hero heart.

01:16.510 --> 01:18.946
I only hear
the drums of war.

01:18.979 --> 01:20.648
[ Grunts ]

01:20.681 --> 01:22.116
What drums?

01:22.150 --> 01:23.451
No!

01:23.484 --> 01:25.653
[ Grunts ]
Finn!

01:25.686 --> 01:29.323
You're hurting me
physically and emotionally.

01:31.159 --> 01:32.760
[ Grunts ]
Oh.

01:32.793 --> 01:34.128
Fight, fight...

01:34.162 --> 01:35.663
Dang it, Finn.

01:35.696 --> 01:38.166
Becoming a crazy,
fiery bad boy

01:38.199 --> 01:40.100
has made you
even more of a babe.

01:40.134 --> 01:42.170
Ice King:
Check it out, LSP.

01:42.203 --> 01:43.304
Wha?

01:43.337 --> 01:46.174
It's a real
magic flying carpet.

01:46.207 --> 01:47.975
I feel just like
Scheherazade.

01:48.008 --> 01:50.644
Lump creature,
did you get the fire jewel?

01:50.678 --> 01:53.614
No.
Flame Princess freakin' ate it.

01:53.647 --> 01:56.083
And now the fire guys are
attacking the Candy Kingdom

01:56.116 --> 01:58.652
because they took everything
I said the wrong way.

01:58.686 --> 02:00.421
And that's totally on them.

02:00.454 --> 02:03.524
But also, we lost Finn
to the flames of war!

02:03.557 --> 02:05.159
Okay.

02:05.193 --> 02:07.828
I'll go find him.

02:07.861 --> 02:09.163
Finn?

02:09.197 --> 02:10.364
Finn?

02:10.398 --> 02:12.866
Oh, where are you, pal?

02:15.035 --> 02:16.670
[ Gasps ]

02:16.704 --> 02:17.805
It's Gunther.

02:17.838 --> 02:19.207
He's in flames, too.

02:19.240 --> 02:22.009
We have to rub soothing lotion
on Guntzy.

02:22.042 --> 02:23.377
You got any lotion?

02:23.411 --> 02:26.180
Your skin is so hydrated.

02:26.214 --> 02:28.216
Fun: Hmm.

02:28.249 --> 02:31.352
Got any...

02:31.385 --> 02:33.321
Caramel Crunch Pies?

02:33.354 --> 02:35.122
[ Groans ]

02:35.155 --> 02:36.890
[ Laughs ]
Yes!

02:36.924 --> 02:40.127
Oh, man, I don't
think you should play
this game ever again.

02:40.160 --> 02:42.530
You're too good at it.

02:42.563 --> 02:44.198
What is that sound?

02:44.232 --> 02:48.569
[ Drums beating in distance ]

02:48.602 --> 02:52.139
Ooh, company's coming!

02:52.172 --> 02:55.909
♪♪

02:55.943 --> 02:57.144
[ Both cheering ]

02:57.177 --> 02:58.412
Whoo!

02:58.446 --> 03:00.481
-Whoo!
-Yes!

03:00.514 --> 03:03.150
Mm! Look at all
these thirsty customers!

03:03.183 --> 03:04.184
[ Ding! ]

03:04.218 --> 03:06.720
Ooh, the pies are ready!

03:06.754 --> 03:10.691
Mm! Ice-cream pies
for all our hot new friends!

03:11.259 --> 03:12.893
Aah!

03:12.926 --> 03:16.730
[ Sizzling ]

03:16.764 --> 03:19.767
[ Both laughing ]

03:19.800 --> 03:21.402
Whoa!
Mm!

03:21.435 --> 03:26.039
♪♪

03:26.073 --> 03:28.442
[ Sizzle! ]

03:29.777 --> 03:31.712
Maybe they don't
like lemonade.

03:31.745 --> 03:33.947
[ Laughs ]

03:33.981 --> 03:36.717
♪♪

03:36.750 --> 03:41.021
Gunther,
your ride is here.

03:41.054 --> 03:42.456
[ Foosh! ]

03:43.657 --> 03:46.427
Gee, who sneezed
in your corn flakes?

03:46.460 --> 03:50.230
He's gone.
The fire has taken his mind.

03:50.264 --> 03:52.533
Is this true, Goontz?

03:52.566 --> 03:54.602
Wenk! Wenk! Wenk!

03:54.635 --> 03:57.070
[ Flame Crowd grunting ]

03:57.104 --> 04:00.941
Look, weird lady,
I don't know you and
you don't know me,

04:00.974 --> 04:02.943
but we're the only
sane people left

04:02.976 --> 04:04.978
in this crazy,
mixed-up world.

04:05.012 --> 04:06.414
Or maybe the world's fine

04:06.447 --> 04:08.649
and we're the ones
losing our marbles.

04:08.682 --> 04:11.885
Either way, it's up to us
to save the day.

04:11.919 --> 04:12.953
Simon.

04:12.986 --> 04:16.657
So, let's get in there
and mash their potatoes.

04:16.690 --> 04:19.993
You got any mashed potatoes?
I'm hungry.

04:20.027 --> 04:21.929
[ Both scream ]

04:21.962 --> 04:23.397
Nerds.

04:23.431 --> 04:25.633
[ Panting ]

04:25.666 --> 04:26.967
I have to hurry.

04:27.000 --> 04:29.303
All this chaos and mayhem
is just -- ugh!

04:29.337 --> 04:31.305
Finn!

04:31.339 --> 04:33.574
You have to stop this.

04:33.607 --> 04:35.075
Think of Jake.

04:35.108 --> 04:38.145
How are you going to fix him
if you're a fire bozo?

04:38.178 --> 04:41.349
And if not for Jake,
do it for me.

04:41.382 --> 04:43.651
Aah!
Oh, my side.

04:43.684 --> 04:45.819
Flame Crowd: [ Chanting ]
Nerds, nerds, smash the nerds!

04:45.853 --> 04:48.255
A nerdless world
is the best kind of world!

04:48.288 --> 04:50.324
Nerd, nerds, no more nerds!
[ Bubblegum humming ]

04:50.358 --> 04:53.527
My children
have come home.

04:53.561 --> 04:55.629
We've come for you!

04:55.663 --> 04:58.666
Oh, a dragon, how fun!

04:58.699 --> 05:01.402
I can do a dragon.
Look.

05:02.503 --> 05:03.704
[ Roars ]

05:03.737 --> 05:06.173
I see you've been playing
with matches.

05:06.206 --> 05:07.841
Fight me, nerd!

05:08.876 --> 05:10.878
[ Giggles ]

05:11.879 --> 05:13.213
Whoo-hoo-hoo!
[ Giggles ]

05:13.246 --> 05:17.050
Are we wrasslin'?
Fun!

05:17.718 --> 05:21.221
[ Giggling ]
[ Grunting ]

05:21.254 --> 05:24.091
Aah!
Stop having fun!

05:25.225 --> 05:27.194
Huh?
[ Gasps ]

05:27.227 --> 05:29.162
Finn, no!

05:29.196 --> 05:30.364
Yah!

05:30.398 --> 05:31.865
This isn't you!
[ Grunts ]

05:31.899 --> 05:35.002
You're being
a very naughty boy, Finn!

05:35.035 --> 05:36.203
Oh, Glob.

05:36.236 --> 05:39.507
Everyone I know
is spazzing out on each other.

05:39.540 --> 05:41.542
They're spazzing each other
to death!

05:41.575 --> 05:43.010
[ Foosh! ]

05:45.078 --> 05:46.547
[ Foosh! ]

05:46.580 --> 05:49.583
Is this the end?

05:49.617 --> 05:51.218
Will I be the last witness

05:51.251 --> 05:54.722
to the glory of this world
that I chose above all others?

05:54.755 --> 05:57.725
[ Marshmaline giggling ]

05:57.758 --> 05:59.893
Tickle, tickle, tickle.
[ Giggles ]

06:03.397 --> 06:04.432
[ Gasps ]

06:04.465 --> 06:08.201
Marceline!
I got you!

06:08.235 --> 06:10.337
[ Splat! ]

06:10.370 --> 06:11.672
[ Groans ]

06:11.705 --> 06:13.441
I got burned.

06:13.474 --> 06:14.875
[ Laughs weakly ]

06:14.908 --> 06:16.910
Oh, Marcy.

06:16.944 --> 06:19.680
I don't think I can
save the world on my own.

06:19.713 --> 06:22.182
I'm more of an aspiring hero
than a real one.

06:22.215 --> 06:26.454
I got, like, the morals and
the charisma and the good looks,

06:26.487 --> 06:29.923
but I lack field experience!

06:29.957 --> 06:33.794
Why couldn't I just get morphed
like everyone else?

06:33.827 --> 06:36.764
Curse these superior genes!

06:37.598 --> 06:38.599
[ Laughs ]

06:38.632 --> 06:40.601
Have some marshmallow,
dude.

06:40.634 --> 06:42.770
It'll calm you down.

06:42.803 --> 06:44.237
Mm.

06:45.906 --> 06:48.041
[ Slurps ]
Mmm.

06:48.075 --> 06:49.943
[ Munches ]

06:49.977 --> 06:54.515
[ Inhales, exhales deeply ]

06:56.183 --> 06:59.920
[ Softly ] Your face
tastes like my happy place.

06:59.953 --> 07:01.254
Fire Finn: Rah!
[ Sword swings ]

07:01.288 --> 07:02.590
[ Gasps ]

07:02.623 --> 07:03.624
Ahh!

07:03.657 --> 07:04.792
Fire Finn rules!

07:04.825 --> 07:08.729
[ Grunting ]
Hah...hah...hah.

07:08.762 --> 07:11.131
It's time
to go professional.

07:11.164 --> 07:13.834
Hah...hah...yah.

07:13.867 --> 07:15.168
Finn!

07:15.202 --> 07:16.837
My little sugarplum.

07:16.870 --> 07:19.973
You've returned to accept
your sweet fate.

07:20.007 --> 07:21.642
I ain't sweet!

07:21.675 --> 07:23.644
I'm a pure warrior
with guns,

07:23.677 --> 07:26.413
and I'ma murder you
for funs!

07:26.446 --> 07:28.315
Rahhh!

07:28.348 --> 07:29.983
No!

07:30.017 --> 07:33.286
You can't stab
a person you love, Finn!

07:33.320 --> 07:35.188
I'll stab you!

07:35.222 --> 07:36.724
-Aah!
-Oof!

07:38.325 --> 07:39.960
Hmm.

07:39.993 --> 07:42.530
I'm sending you
to your...

07:42.563 --> 07:44.197
happy place!

07:44.231 --> 07:45.265
[ Sizzle! ]

07:45.298 --> 07:47.635
[ Sniffs, snorts ]

07:47.668 --> 07:51.705
♪♪

07:52.506 --> 07:55.042
Here, take it,
you cutie.

07:57.010 --> 07:58.011
Rawr!

07:58.045 --> 08:01.014
LSP: [ Echoing ]
I said your happy place.

08:01.048 --> 08:04.518
Happy place!

08:04.552 --> 08:08.021
I wish
I could stay like this.

08:08.055 --> 08:09.156
[ Foosh! ]

08:09.189 --> 08:10.691
[ Sizzle! ]

08:10.724 --> 08:13.060
I've enjoyed
just -- just hanging out.

08:13.093 --> 08:15.729
Me too.

08:21.569 --> 08:25.072
[ Soft sizzling ]

08:25.105 --> 08:26.574
You did it, LSP.

08:26.607 --> 08:28.976
I'm human Finn.

08:29.009 --> 08:31.411
There's no time for romance,
Finn.

08:31.444 --> 08:33.681
We got to get that jewel.

08:33.714 --> 08:35.048
Oh, yeah.

08:35.082 --> 08:36.416
Hup!

08:36.449 --> 08:38.719
I'm bringing you back,
Bonnie.

08:38.752 --> 08:40.554
[ Giggles ]

08:40.588 --> 08:42.222
That's sweet.

08:42.255 --> 08:43.490
Hup.

08:43.523 --> 08:44.725
Aah!

08:44.758 --> 08:48.896
Sweet,
but not sweet enough.

08:48.929 --> 08:51.231
[ Both screaming ]
[ Giggling ]

08:51.264 --> 08:52.633
Eeh!

08:53.366 --> 08:54.401
Ugh!

08:54.434 --> 08:59.239
[ Rumbling, Bubblegum grunting ]

08:59.272 --> 09:02.109
This charade
has run its course.

09:02.142 --> 09:06.680
In your hearts,
you are all sweet.

09:06.714 --> 09:11.585
♪ Let me call you sweetheart

09:11.619 --> 09:15.923
♪ I'm in love with you

09:15.956 --> 09:17.090
Wenk.

09:17.124 --> 09:20.193
♪ Let me hear you whisper
[ Gasping ]

09:20.227 --> 09:21.695
Let my impervious bod
be your shield!

09:21.729 --> 09:24.131
♪ That you love me, too
Mmm!

09:24.164 --> 09:26.366
[ Screams ]

09:26.399 --> 09:29.569
♪ Keep the love-light glowing
No!

09:29.603 --> 09:30.704
[ Gasps ]
Flame Princess!

09:30.738 --> 09:33.406
♪ In your eyes so true

09:33.440 --> 09:35.609
[ Coughs ]
Phoebe?

09:35.643 --> 09:38.245
♪ Let me call you sweetheart
[ Candy rattling ]

09:38.278 --> 09:39.446
[ Gags ]

09:39.479 --> 09:43.751
♪ I'm in love with you

09:43.784 --> 09:44.785
The final jujubee.

09:44.818 --> 09:46.319
Betty: Finn!

09:48.088 --> 09:50.557
Mm-hmm.

09:50.590 --> 09:51.625
Hmm.

09:51.659 --> 09:54.127
[ Gobbling ]

09:54.161 --> 09:58.065
Purple clump,
you are a sour anomaly.

09:58.098 --> 09:59.066
Whuh?

09:59.099 --> 10:00.500
[ Muffled ]
What'd you call me?

10:00.533 --> 10:03.804
[ Candy rattling ]
Aah!

10:03.837 --> 10:06.974
Give me them jewels, Finn.
We're out of time.

10:07.007 --> 10:08.341
Give me, give me, give me.

10:08.375 --> 10:09.509
Here.

10:09.542 --> 10:11.144
[ Cackles ]

10:11.178 --> 10:14.481
Now, let's grab LSP
and get the buns out of here --

10:14.514 --> 10:16.116
Hoh.

10:16.149 --> 10:17.484
Huh?

10:17.517 --> 10:23.757
[ Cackling ]

10:23.791 --> 10:25.192
[ Ting! ]

10:26.059 --> 10:27.995
I've been betrayed.

10:28.028 --> 10:30.197
I've been Betty-trayed!

10:30.230 --> 10:32.032
[ Rustling ]

10:33.300 --> 10:34.802
[ Screams ]

10:34.835 --> 10:38.338
♪ Let me
call you sweetheart ♪

10:38.371 --> 10:42.542
Together:
♪ I'm in love with you

10:42.575 --> 10:46.046
♪ Let me hear you whisper

10:46.079 --> 10:48.949
♪ That you love me, too

10:48.982 --> 10:50.317
[ Screams ]

10:50.350 --> 10:53.553
All:
♪ Keep the love-light glowing

10:53.586 --> 10:58.191
♪ In your eyes so true

10:58.225 --> 11:01.695
♪ Let me call you sweetheart

11:01.729 --> 11:06.333
♪ I'm in love with you

11:09.169 --> 11:13.040
♪ Come along with me

11:13.073 --> 11:16.877
♪ And the butterflies and bees
